{"title":"教你沉迷学习","uid":"63fa495fec6c62629390191be21ecbe3","slug":"教你沉迷学习","date":"2023-09-01T14:09:32.000Z","updated":"2023-09-01T14:21:38.106Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/教你沉迷学习.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/09/01/pPBid0O.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"如何沉迷学习-心流\"><a href=\"#如何沉迷学习-心流\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"如何沉迷学习-心流\"></a>如何沉迷学习-心流</h1><p>具体请见b站视频链接：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fV4y1R7Kg/?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0&vd_source=2d7aee534c0106401a858a7d6e7c51b3\">“虚假的快乐”是怎么控制你的？</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>原理：</p>\n<p>内驱的动力来自于多巴胺（对于成果、积极结果的欲望），而在被外部强行提供任务时，就引发去甲肾上腺素的分泌，这使得人焦虑紧张</p>\n<p>由于去甲对于人体有害，所以会分泌皮质醇，使得人没有动力</p>\n<p><strong>conclusion：把工作当成自己提升自己的机会，而提升自己的能力是一种创作</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/img1.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>如何精进自我</p>\n<ul>\n<li>行动有<strong>明确目标</strong>（可以分解大目标为具体的事情，最好可以<strong>量化任务，记得</strong>​<strong>加ddl</strong>） ———–语言的模糊&#x2F;抽象即为熵增</li>\n<li>行动有所挑战（不至于特别难）</li>\n<li>行动结果有<strong>及时反馈</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>降噪</p>\n<p>人最大的痛苦并非求之不得，而是既要又要</p>\n<p>为自己心中<strong>坚定的目标做出高亮</strong>，对其他的目标说<strong>“那不重要！”</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>‍</p>\n","text":"那就是...心流大法啦~！...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":326,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"thoughts","slug":"thoughts","count":2,"path":"api/categories/thoughts.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"thoughts","slug":"thoughts","count":2,"path":"api/tags/thoughts.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0-%E5%BF%83%E6%B5%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">如何沉迷学习-心流</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"一只小知更鸟","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img1.imgtp.com/2023/08/29/RZ7FZ0Cx.png","link":"/","description":"大三狗在读,缓慢探索博客中...<br />热爱coding与控制,吉他画画也会一些~","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu"